  "title": "Cashier cum Service Crew (Family Karaoke)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u><br />Working Hours: Day Shift, 1 pm – 10 pm</p><ul><li><p>Provide friendly and courteous customer service</p></li><li><p>Handle reservations, phone calls, and customer inquiries</p></li><li><p>Check in customers and prepare karaoke rooms for bookings</p></li><li><p>Handle cashier duties and ensure cash accuracy at the start/end of shift</p></li><li><p>Assist customers with the karaoke system and song selection (training provided)</p></li><li><p>Take orders, input into the POS system, and serve food & beverages</p></li><li><p>Maintain a clean, safe, and tidy environment</p></li><li><p>Follow food safety and hygiene standards</p></li><li><p>Work independently and communicate well with team members</p></li><li><p>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned</p></li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li><p>Fluent in English</p></li><li><p>Team player with a service-oriented attitude</p></li></ul><p><u><strong>Work Schedule:</strong></u></p><ul><li><p>6 days off per month</p></li><li><p>Paid overtime if required</p></li></ul><p><u><strong>Benefits:</strong></u></p><ul><li><p>OT, commission, tips & variable bonuses</p></li><li><p>Outpatient medical consultation benefit</p></li><li><p>Night shift transport provided</p></li></ul><p></p><p></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
